*Fender blackface Super Reverbs – With four 10&quot; speakers.
*Fender Hot Rod Deluxe

*Fender Vibro Kings – With three 10&quot; speakers&#x27;
*Fender Vibro King Custom
*Fender Hot Rod DeVilles
*Fuchs ODS 50 -used at 2012 Grammys

